data.description: Turn key all brick ranch with detached 2.5 car garage. Open concept living space with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and full finished basement. Remodeled kitchen with granite counters and tons of cabinet space is open to living and dining room. Wood flooring throughout and lots of natural light. Full finished basement includes family room, full bath and separate laundry room with storage area. Fully fenced yard with brick pavers and screened in porch, perfect for summer entertaining. Close to schools, shopping, highways.
